        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks JM for bill for £480 and sends receipt. Number of copies differs in note and in receipt (2500 and 2000, respectively). Not surprised sale is slackening; number printed was bold. Reminds JM to advertise "with additions and corrections".</p> 
<p>Will consult JM on illustrations for <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
